title: DWMAGIC Summit Dishwasher Cleaner
description:
Summit Brands Dishwasher Magic DWMAGIC

● #1 Selling Brand in Dishwasher Cleaning
● Only EPA Registered Disinfectant Dishwasher Cleaner
● A Clean Dishwasher Equals Clean Dishes
● Maximizes Cleaning Performance & Improves Life Span of Dishwasher
● Cleans Your Dishes Better
● Improve Water Jet Circulation
● Lower Electrical Consumption of your Dishwasher
● Lessens the Risk of Break Down

Product Information

Leftover food waste & stains can lead to the formation of harmful bacteria. DISHWASHER MAGIC is an EPA Registered Disinfectant designed to kill 99.9% of harmful bacteria in the dishwasher.

Over time, your dishwasher can lose its cleaning effectiveness due to build-up of lime, calcium, rust, grease and detergent residue. DISHWASHER MAGIC is scientifically formulated to eliminate all forms of build-up in your dishwasher.

AVAILABLE SIZES: 12 fl. oz.

)Removes build–up 
)Disinfecting to kill harmful bacteria 
Dishwasher Magic cleans the food oils, minerals, and soap build-up from the filter screen, pump, and jets. This build–up starves the pump of the water supply needed to effectively clean the dishes. Dishwasher Magic's disinfection properties kill harmful gram negative bacteria like e–coli & salmonella. No other dishwasher cleaner both cleans and disinfects your dishwasher. 

Cleaning Tips
(Please follow cautions and instructions on the label carefully.)

For use in Automatic Dishwashers.

DISHWASHER MAGIC is safe for all dishwasher model interiors, plumbing and septic systems.

Regular cleaning of your dishwasher is recommended by all manufacturers to maintain cleaning performance.

DIRECTIONS FOR USE
Start with empty dishwasher. Do not use with dishwashing detergent. Remove cap. DO NOT REMOVE WAX PLUG. Place bottle upside down inside the silverware basket or in a secure position in the bottom rack. Close dishwasher, run machine on hottest cycle. (i.e. pots & pans, heavy duty, etc.). Note water must be as hot as possible to melt wax plug. For best results, first run faucet nearest to dishwasher with hot water. For heavy build up, a second application of DISHWASHER MAGIC may be required.

Use once a month to maintain your dishwasher and prevent build-up.

title: Forearm Forklift Lifting Straps
description:
Forearm Forklift Lifting Straps® : 4ARMC

A pair of patented straps that employ leverage. They make the appliances you carry seem 66% lighter. Also encourages proper lifting techniques. 

Cleverly called the Forearm Forklift, these handy adjustable lifting straps make carrying heavy and hard-to-handle furniture and appliances remarkably easy. Using the Forearm Forklift, two people can carry large, heavy objects at a low center of gravity, only inches off the ground.
As a result, you don't have to bend way down to pick up the object, and
you don't have to stoop awkwardly to clear doorways. The Forearm Forklift
also helps you move objects over sensitive floors such as wood, vinyl,
or tile without the same risk of causing scuffs or damage.

- Comes with 2 straps
- Both straps are adjustable up to 48” 
- Includes easy-to-use & illustrated instructions
- Rated for carrying up to 700 lbs. 

- JUST X-CROSS THE STRAPS UNDERNEATH THE ITEM THAT YOU'RE CARRYING AND THEY NEVER SLIP OUT
